**Iteration:** 2 (verifies iter-1 closures + new issues introduced by v2 revision).
**Date:** 2026-04-27.
**Reviewers:** Codex (gpt-5.4 xhigh), Opus (claude opus xhigh). Gemini quota-exhausted (9th iter in a row).

